<br>
For one of the wrist slots, I intend to purchase a Bracelet of Comprehension.  Should it be advisable to purchase for the other two slots, I was thinking of either a Golden Bracer (which provides Extended Range II) or a Golden Chitin Bracer for the second wrist slot.  In the shoulder slot, I was focusing on the Fancy Velvet Mantle (which also provides Extended Range II).  If I purchased the mantle, I would go with the GCB over the GB for the wrist slot, not wanted to pay to duplicate Extended Range II.  Other options for the shoulders would be Jade Inlaid Spaulders or an Elder Wolf Hide.  (I have been searching for both the Piranha Scale Mask – for the shoulders in spite of its name – and the Tainted Skin Shroud, but thus far have never found them for sale in the bazaar on my server, Lanys.  Both of these would be superior to all of the other shoulder slot choices that I’ve mentioned if I could simply find them.)<br>
<br>
I would appreciate any advice you have to offer on these focus item slots or any other you might want to mention.  I don’t want to purchase items that are not needed, but do want to outfit my new character as best as I am able.<br>
<br>
I am really excited about trying my hand at a new type of character and want to do it as intelligently as possible from the start.  Thank you for your time.  It is appreciated!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=calfhigh>Calfhigh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#333333>(12/30/02 8:20:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1144.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Summoned vs. Purchased Equipment</span><hr size=1> at 65 i still use the ring earring and bracer when ever im not in resist gear those 3 slots i change in when i need resists.<br>
